                                    <h1 class="header__title" >
                        How to Use Thoughts of Immortality to Awaken Your True Self
                    </h1>
                
                                    <h2 class="header__subtitle">
                        Realize the divinity of your eternal soul.
                    </h2>
                            </div>
        </div>

                                


                                
    
    





        
    
